{"captions":[{"content":"我喜欢树木，而且非常幸运的是","startTime":0,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"我们住在一个非常棒的植物园的附近。","startTime":3000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"星期天的时候，我通常会和我夫人","startTime":6000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"现在是和我四岁的孩子，","startTime":9000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"一起爬树，玩捉迷藏。","startTime":11000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"我上的第二所学校也有不少大树","startTime":14000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"那儿有棵奇异的郁金香树，我认为它是国内最大的一棵。","startTime":18000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"在它和操场的周围，","startTime":22000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"还有很多很棒的灌木和植物。","startTime":26000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"有一天我被一些同学抓住，带进灌木丛里","startTime":28000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":true},{"content":"我被剥光了衣服，我受到攻击，","startTime":32000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"我被虐待，这一切来得那么突然。","startTime":36000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"好了，我之所以那么说，是因为事后，我觉得，","startTime":41000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"嗯，当我返回学校时，我感到肮脏，觉得受到了背叛，","startTime":45000,"duration":6000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"我觉得耻辱，但更主要的是--我感到很无力。","startTime":51000,"duration":5000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"三十年后我坐在一架飞机里，","startTime":58000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"邻座的是一位来自智利的女士，维罗妮卡。","startTime":61000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"我们参加了一个人权之旅，","startTime":64000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"她开始向我诉说被折磨是什么样的感觉，","startTime":67000,"duration":5000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"并且从我特有的立场出发，","startTime":72000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"这是我有的唯一的参照点。","startTime":75000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"那是一个神奇的学习历程，","startTime":79000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"因为对我而言，人权问题是一件","startTime":81000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"你明白，业余的兴趣；但主要来说，","startTime":84000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"它是发生在远方的其他人身上的事。","startTime":87000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"但是我在1985年接到了波诺的电话","startTime":90000,"duration":7000,"startOfParagraph":true},{"content":"你们知道，他是个优秀的歌手，但他是个惊人的说服者，","startTime":97000,"duration":5000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"（笑声）","startTime":102000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":true},{"content":"我很难对他说不。","startTime":104000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":true},{"content":"在我刚做完歌曲\"Biko\"后，他说，","startTime":107000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"我们正要给“特赦”组织做一个巡演，","startTime":109000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"你一定得参与。于是，那是第一次我真正地","startTime":111000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"出来开始认识一些人","startTime":114000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"他们曾看着自己的家人在自己面前被枪杀，","startTime":118000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"配偶在飞机上被扔进大海里","startTime":121000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"突然之间，人权的世界来到了我的世界，","startTime":124000,"duration":5000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"我再也不能像以前那样袖手旁观了。","startTime":129000,"duration":5000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"所以我开始参与到为“特赦”办的巡演中，","startTime":134000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":true},{"content":"并在1988年取代波诺开始学习鼓动别人。","startTime":138000,"duration":5000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"我不如他做得好，但是我也成功地使尤索·恩多、斯汀、","startTime":143000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"特蕾西·查普曼、布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀为“特赦”做环球巡演，","startTime":147000,"duration":5000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"这是个神奇的经历。","startTime":152000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"再一次，我收获了一份异乎寻常的教育，","startTime":155000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"并且我第一次真正地","startTime":159000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"结识不同国家的许多人","startTime":161000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"有关人权的故事变得活生生起来，","startTime":165000,"duration":5000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"再一次，我不能允许自己袖手旁观。","startTime":170000,"duration":6000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"但最让我惊异的是，我并不知道","startTime":176000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":true},{"content":"一个人可以这样地受苦，","startTime":179000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"然后你的全部体验，你的故事，遭到否认","startTime":182000,"duration":6000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"被掩盖，被遗忘。","startTime":188000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"然而，好像一旦有照相机或摄像机在","startTime":191000,"duration":5000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"或这","startTime":196000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"那些当权者想要掩盖这些故事就变得难了很多。","startTime":199000,"duration":6000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"锐步在这些\"人权，现在！\"巡演后设立了一个基金会","startTime":206000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"并且当时决定","startTime":210000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"恩，我们在几年中提议","startTime":214000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"想要努力设立一个部门","startTime":217000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"给人权活动家派发相机。","startTime":219000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"事实上它无疾而终，","startTime":224000,"duration":1000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"之后发生了那个Rodney King事件","startTime":225000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"人们觉得如果你在恰当的时间恰当的地点有个相机，","startTime":228000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"或许是错误的时间，取决于你是谁，","startTime":231000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"那么你真的可以开始做些事情，","startTime":235000,"duration":5000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"开始发起运动，开始让别人听见自己的声音，","startTime":240000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"告诉别人发生了什么事。","startTime":244000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"所以，“目击者”在1992年被建立了","startTime":246000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":true},{"content":"从此之后一共在六十多个国家派发相机。","startTime":250000,"duration":6000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"我们和活动家团体一起开展运动，","startTime":256000,"duration":6000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"帮助他们讲述故事","startTime":262000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"一会儿我将给你们展示一个最新的运动，","startTime":266000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"我恐怕它是来自乌干达的一个故事，","startTime":270000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"尽管我们昨天听到了来自乌干达的一个精彩故事，","startTime":273000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"这一个就没那么美好了。","startTime":277000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"在乌干达北部，","startTime":279000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"有将近一百五十万流离失所的人","startTime":281000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"他们并非外国的难民，","startTime":284000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"而是因为长达将近20年的内战","startTime":287000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"而颠沛流离的人们。","startTime":291000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"两万孩子被迫成为童军","startTime":293000,"duration":6000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"国际罪犯法庭在追捕五个头目","startTime":299000,"duration":8000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"他们来自，那个","startTime":307000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"恩，那个军队叫什么来着，","startTime":309000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"应该是国王反击队","startTime":311000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"而他们的政府也不是廉洁公正的。","startTime":314000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"让我们来看看这第一段录像。","startTime":316000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"（音乐）","startTime":318000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":true},{"content":"女：在难民营里的日子从不好过，直至今日也是如此。","startTime":321000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"我们之所以会留在营中，是因为惧怕逼我们进营的那些因素，","startTime":324000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"依然在家乡猖獗。","startTime":328000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"文字：“双重烈焰：乌干达北部的酷刑折磨和颠沛流离”","startTime":334000,"duration":7000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"男：当我们在家乡时，是Kony的叛乱的士兵在骚扰我们。","startTime":345000,"duration":7000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"一开始的时候我们在营里还是安全的。","startTime":352000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"但是后来政府的士兵开始虐待我们。","startTime":355000,"duration":5000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"（齐唱）","startTime":360000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":true},{"content":"Jennifer:一个士兵走过来，问我们去哪儿了。","startTime":363000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"Evelyn和我藏在妈妈身后","startTime":367000,"duration":6000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"Eveyln:他命令我们坐下，所以我们只好坐下","startTime":373000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"另一个士兵也走了过来","startTime":376000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"Jennifer:那个男人走过来脱我的衣服。","startTime":379000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"另一个把Evelyn带向一边","startTime":383000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"那个玷污了我的人又走向Evelyn，糟蹋了她。","startTime":386000,"duration":5000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"那个强暴Evelyn的人则走过来侮辱我。","startTime":391000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"男人：士兵们拿着这么长的棍子拷打我们，严刑逼供。","startTime":395000,"duration":8000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"打我们的时候，他们不停地说，“说实话！”","startTime":403000,"duration":12000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"女人：他们坚持说我在撒谎。","startTime":415000,"duration":5000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"那时，他们开枪射下了我的手指","startTime":420000,"duration":5000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"我跌倒了。他们跑回队伍，留着我在那儿等死。","startTime":425000,"duration":9000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"（音乐）","startTime":438000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":true},{"content":"文字：乌干达在1986年批准了禁止酷刑公约","startTime":440000,"duration":9000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"酷刑的定义是任何官方为了获取信息或供词","startTime":449000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"co